      "title": "A protest in Galle",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A demonstration organized by Janatha Vimukti Peramuna is currently being held in front of Galle bus station.",
        "This protest has been named as \"Pannuwa is not over, rallying for a new mandate\" and a large number of people will participate in the protest."
